caption:
Our 12-min feature just dropped on @yahoofinance homepage 😱 — and this one personally means the world to me. It’s about finding my way towards embodying my heart-forward, sensitive side, even as a leader experiencing my own whirlwind of self-doubt and scarcity. I’m given space to vulnerably share my hard-earned lessons as CEO of @omsom, beyond just the wins. A lot of gratitude for the brilliant @brookedipalma for going a few levels deeper with me, and even asking about my family 🥹⁣
⁣
The upcoming episodes of Lead this Way will feature the CEOs of General Motors, New Balance, among others — so stay tuned for those! Video linked in bio ❤️
